00:35:22.050 --> 00:35:23.650
So we want to draw
the band diagram,

00:35:23.650 --> 00:35:25.880
just to make sure
everybody's in the same page.

00:35:25.880 --> 00:35:27.255
So we're going to
be starting out

00:35:27.255 --> 00:35:32.820
with our valence band and our
conduction band over here.

00:35:32.820 --> 00:35:35.550
And as we move toward
our space charge region,

00:35:35.550 --> 00:35:38.700
as we move toward our depletion
region, our transition region

00:35:38.700 --> 00:35:42.780
here in the middle, we're
going to see some effect.

00:35:42.780 --> 00:35:45.910
We're going to see some bending
of the bands, if you will.

00:35:45.910 --> 00:35:48.120
So your question
