00:41:51.469 --> 00:41:52.260
PROFESSOR: Exactly.

00:41:52.260 --> 00:41:53.968
We are opposing the
field that was set up

00:41:53.968 --> 00:41:56.900
by the balance of the drift and
diffusion currents initially.

00:41:56.900 --> 00:41:57.872
Yeah.

00:41:57.872 --> 00:41:59.573
AUDIENCE: Under
