01:01:30.160 --> 01:01:32.440
Densities of
electrons and holes.

01:01:32.440 --> 01:01:33.940
And unfortunately,
I'm going to have

01:01:33.940 --> 01:01:35.880
to move rather quickly
through these slides.

01:01:35.880 --> 01:01:40.360
This is the essence of
why a solar cell behaves

01:01:40.360 --> 01:01:41.440
like a diode.

01:01:41.440 --> 01:01:43.180
And it's really
something that is best

01:01:43.180 --> 01:01:45.830
done by studying on your own.

01:01:45.830 --> 01:01:48.440
I'm happy to walk you through
